  <p class="muted">Customer retention analysis using R with churn models and a translated retention strategy.</p>

  <h2>Methods</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Feature engineering + data wrangling in R</li>
    <li>Model training: logistic regression, decision tree, random forest</li>
    <li>Evaluation: cross-validation + performance comparison</li>
    <li>Business translation: churn drivers → actionable retention plan</li>
